Introduction to Polymer Chemistry, Wiley, New York, 1962; F. Bueche, Physical Properties of Polymers, Intersclence, New York, 1962; and W. R. Sorenson andT. W.
Campbell, Preparative Methods of Polymer Chemistry, Interscience, New York, 1961.
